FTK == Funny ToolKit (Write just for fun)
=====================================================
(You can use it in commercial software, but please let me know.)

How to build ftk from svn source code?
=====================================================
o download:
  svn checkout http://ftk.googlecode.com/svn/trunk/ ftk-read-only

o configure:
  cd ftk-read-only
  ./autogen.sh
  ./configure --with-backend=linux-x11:320x480
  (run ./configure --help for more options)

o build:
  make

o run:
  cd src/demos
  ./demo_button
 

XUL = XML UI Language
=====================================================
o supported widget
  label
  entry
  button
  wait_box
  progress_bar
  radio_group
  radio_button
  check_button
  image
  scroll_bar
  window
  dialog

o supported attribute
  x 
  y
  w
  h
  id
  attr
  value
  visible
  max_value
  page_delta
  checked
  bg[normal]
  bg[active]
  bg[focused]
  bg[disable]
  bg_image[normal]
  bg_image[disable]
  bg_image[active]
  bg_image[focused]
  fg[normal]
  fg[active]
  fg[focused]
  fg[disable]

o supported variable, variable preceeded with '$'
  pw/parent_width
  ph/parent_height
  ww/window_width
  wh/window_height
  dw/display_width
  dh/display_height
  FTK_ATTR_TRANSPARENT
  FTK_ATTR_BG_CENTER
  FTK_ATTR_BG_TILE
  FTK_ATTR_BG_FOUR_CORNER
  FTK_ATTR_NO_FOCUS
  FTK_ATTR_INSENSITIVE
  FTK_ATTR_FOCUSED

